item.content:encoded: Posting the photo, Neymar wrote, ‘Brother, it didn’t go the way we thought it would, but we tried our best. It was a pleasure to spend two more years with you. Good luck with the new chapter. from good I love you.’ Messi wrote in the comments section, ‘Thank you Neymar. Whatever remained, we once again enjoyed playing together, sharing the days. Good luck to you. You’re a beautiful person with a great demeanor, and that’s all that matters at the end of the day. I love you so much.’
